{
  "text": "where the wavevector magnitude is given by k 2π∕λ, λ is the wavelength of the incident plane wave associated with the ray, and L is the etalon thickness. Under conditions when θ λ ≪ 1, Eq. (1) can be expanded to second order in θ λ to obtain an approximate dispersion relation [CITATION_1] ",
